name: Bitcoin Pizza 80348
description: This NFT entitles the owner to claim the Bitcoin Pizza #80348 (InscriptionID: f2258440ca345706ac3ddba7974c787ac7a5e129cf06148e30360bb1a5d84de9i0) inscribed on the Bitcoin Blockchain. Ordinals are digital assets inscribed on Satoshis, the lowest denomination of Bitcoin (BTC). Please open a Support Ticket in our Discord to Claim the Pizza. In order to claim the Ordinal, a compatible Bitcoin address is required. Please follow this Tutorial to Setup a compatible Bitcoin Wallet: https://docs.raredough.com/receiving-bitcoin-ordinals
